# MCPB bundle build outputs — mcpb/manifest.json is committed as the
# source-of-truth manifest; the bundled binary and the packaged .mcpb
# archive are reproducible from `cargo build --release` plus the bundling
# step, and are kept out of git history to avoid bloat
mcpb/bin/
mcpb/*.mcpb

# Personal Claude Code agent instructions for this checkout — single-user
# launchd labels, single-instance memory paths, cross-session-context
# pointers calibrated to the author's instance. General operator and
# contributor-facing content lives in README.md; CLAUDE.md remains a
# personal-config artifact, not project source.
CLAUDE.md

# Personal development records — roadmap state, audit/triage/review chain
# forensics per commit, subagent-prompt templates, investigation reports,
# milestones, requirements. Single-instance development workflow artifacts,
# not project source.
.planning/
